    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Suiton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This oddly named technique does not actually have anything to do with eels or talons, and was often used by shinobi of the Hidden Mist when traveling or fighting over water. You gain the effects of the Tadayou and Issui Suberi no Jutsu techniques, without needing to make any checks. You also benefit from Speed Rank 1 while you are on water. The technique ends when you step on land. On the round the technique would end, you can spend 1 Chakra to extend its duration by 1 round.</p>\n\n\n\n",
